definitions.definition: The fourth day of the week in many religious traditions, and the third day of the week in systems using the ISO 8601 norm; it follows Tuesday and precedes Thursday .

main_definition: The fourth day of the week in many religious traditions, and the third day of the week in systems using the ISO 8601 norm; it follows Tuesday and precedes Thursday .

definitions.definition: Nickname of Sheffield Wednesday of the Football League.

main_definition: ( UK , soccer ) Nickname of Sheffield Wednesday of the Football League.
